    <briefdescription>
<para>Descriptor used to configure an <ref refid="class_boon_1_1_application" kindref="compound">Application</ref> instance. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Contains window parameters, application name, content directory and network driver mode. Fill this struct and pass it to the <ref refid="class_boon_1_1_application" kindref="compound">Application</ref> constructor to initialize the runtime. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
